content: Do you know any jokes about coffee drinks?

Sure, here's one for you:

Why don't some couples go to the coffee shop?

Because they prefer to make their own lattes!

Haha, get it? "Lattes" sounds like "laters," meaning "see you later." So, they prefer to say "laters" instead of going out for coffee. It's a bit of a play on words. What do you think?
